message:
From the public meeting at Khanapara, I expressed my gratitude to the people of India for their unwavering support & trust in our Government. I gave a detailed report about our Government’s work in a wide range of sectors & how it is positively  impacting lives.

Over the last three years, we have placed our trust in each & every Indian. 125 crore citizens will power our nation to new heights. http://nm-4.com/z9w4
